## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the evolution of managerial roles. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude insights from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the rapidly changing nature of business environments means that the characteristics of modern managers may continue to evolve, potentially rendering some findings outdated in the near future.

